g.text: locked-amount = sum(offer[@status == OFFERED].offered-amount, offer[@status in (ACCEPTED, PAYED)].accepted-amount)
when o1::Offer becomes OFFERED, then o1.asset.locked-amount += o1.offered-amount
when o1::Offer becomes REJECTED, then o1.asset.locked-amount -= o1.offered-amount
when o1::Offer becomes EXPIRED, then o1.asset.locked-amount -= o1.offered-amount
when o1::Offer becomes ACCEPTED, then o1.asset.locked-amount -= (o1.offered-amount - o1.accepted.amount)
when o1::Offer becomes FINALIZED, then (o1.asset.sold-amount += o1.accepted-amount) and (o1.asset.locked-amount -= o1.accepted-amount)
- Offers need not to be made at the same time.
- Accepted offer can expire before payment.
- Issuer can reserve some portion of issued tokens
- Multiple issuance for a asset - Initial issuance, Additional issuance
